org.ehcache.clustered.client.config

Interface DedicatedClusteredResourcePool

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ClusteredResourcePool, org.ehcache.config.ResourcePool, org.ehcache.config.SizedResourcePool

    public interface DedicatedClusteredResourcePool
extends ClusteredResourcePool, org.ehcache.config.SizedResourcePool
    Specifies a ClusteredResourcePool reserving space from a server-based clustered resource. A FixedClusteredResourcePool uses dedicated space on the server.

      • getFromResource

        java.lang.String getFromResource()
        Identifies the server-side clustered resource from which space for this pool is reserved. If no server resource is identified, the resource identified in the server configuration as the default is used.
